OL,6,FRepresentatives of the Convie and Fox
OL,7,Ffamilies said afterwards they were
OL,8,Fdevastated at the verdict that a man
OL,9,Fhas been found not guilty of the UVF
OL,10,Fmurders of Catholic workmen Eamon Fox
OL,11,Fand Gary Convie in north Belfast in
OL,12,F1994.
OL,14,FJames Stewart Smyth, 58 of Forthriver
OL,15,FLink in Belfast, was also cleared of
OL,16,Fone count of attempted murder,
OL,17,Fpossession of a firearm and membership
OL,18,Fof a proscribed organisation, the UVF.
