OL,6,FMr Convie and Mr Fox were sitting in a
OL,7,Fparked car at a building site when
OL,8,Fthey were shot dead by a gunman
OL,9,Fstanding in an adjacent playground
OL,10,Fbeside North Queen Street in May 1994.
OL,12,FDelivering his judgment in the non-
OL,13,Fjury trial at Belfast Crown Court, Mr
OL,14,FJustice O'Hara said it could not be
OL,15,Fproven beyond reasonable doubt that
OL,16,FSmyth was the gunman.
OL,18,FThe main prosecution witness in the
OL,19,Fcase was UVF man turned loyalist
OL,20,Fsupergrass Gary Haggarty.
