OL,6,FHaggarty was handed a reduced prison
OL,7,Fsentence after admitting more than 500
OL,8,Fterror crimes, including five murders,
OL,9,Fbut he was released from prison in
OL,10,F2018 only four months into the six-and-
OL,11,Fa-half year term, for providing
OL,12,Finformation about other terrorist
OL,13,Fsuspects.
OL,15,FBeginning his judgment, the judge told
OL,16,Fthe court: "The only reason this
OL,17,Fattack took place was that the men
OL,18,Fwere Catholics.
