OL,6,F"In the eyes of the UVF, that was
OL,7,Fenough to make them targets, and easy
OL,8,Ftargets."
OL,10,FHe said the sole issue to be
OL,11,Fconsidered in the case was whether it
OL,12,Fcould be proven beyond reasonable
OL,13,Fdoubt that Smyth had been the gunman
OL,14,Fwho shot Mr Convie and Mr Fox.
OL,16,FHowever, the judge said he had doubts
OL,17,Fabout DNA evidence presented by the
OL,18,Fprosecution.
