OL,6,FThe judge also said that a number of
OL,7,Feyewitnesses had described the gunman
OL,8,Fas being between 5ft 8in to 5ft 10in
OL,9,Fin height, while Smyth is 5ft 4in tall.
OL,11,FMr Justice O'Hara said he could not be
OL,12,Fsatisfied beyond reasonable doubt that
OL,13,FSmyth was the gunman and found him not
OL,14,Fguilty.
OL,16,FHowever, he said that Smyth did not
OL,17,Fleave the court without a stain on his
OL,18,Fcharacter, having been previously
OL,19,Fconvicted of murder.
