OL,6,FSpeaking outside court, Eamon Fox's
OL,7,Fson Kieran was asked if the family's
OL,8,Flast chance of getting justice had
OL,9,Fpassed.
OL,11,FHe said: "As far as the criminal side
OL,12,Fgoes, yes I think it is.
OL,14,F"We are looking at other possibilities
OL,15,Fbecause this is just the tip of an
OL,16,Ficeberg."
OL,18,FHe added: "We thought we had a strong
OL,19,Fcase but the threshold to get a
OL,20,Fconviction in these courts (is so
OL,21,Fhigh).
