OL,6,F"It is heartbreaking. It's a sad day
OL,7,Ffor us."
OL,9,FLawyer for the Convie and Fox
OL,10,Ffamilies, Padraig O'Muirigh, said the
OL,11,Fcase had demonstrated deficiencies in
OL,12,Fthe criminal justice system,
OL,14,FHe said: "The Convie and Fox families
OL,15,Fare devastated by today's verdict.
OL,17,F"It has been a long journey for them
OL,18,Fand a very disappointing end to that.
OL,20,F"The judge identified considerable
OL,21,Flacunas in the prosecution case.
