OL,6,F"I think this case highlights the
OL,7,Fdeficiencies in the criminal justice
OL,8,Fsystem dealing with matters like this
OL,10,F"When you are relying on an assisting
OL,11,Foffender, a convicted criminal in a
OL,12,Fnotorious UVF unit, that is always
OL,13,Fgoing to be highly problematic in a
OL,14,Fcriminal trial."
OL,16,FHe added: "There needs to be another
OL,17,Fprocess where these issues, which are
OL,18,Fof huge public concern, are publicly
OL,19,Fventilated in a proper forum."
